name of bank - LEXOCORP

OBJECTIVE
-Being able to manage financial transactions and offer good services to customers
- The application should be fast and secure
- It should be optimized and also scalable
- 
- Transaction records should be recorded on the admin side
- 



USER
Users should be able to withdraw and deposit money.
Users should be able to transfer money within each other
Users should be able to Sign up for an account and should be able to close their account.
Users should be able to see their transaction history

ADMIN
The admin should be able to see all transaction records
The admin should be able to freeze their account
The admin should be able to log in and log out
The admin can not see password of users.
The admin should also have a developer option.


